        <p>校园到职场：理论知识的"落地"阵痛</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="177.36" topLeftX="70.12" topLeftY="340.68" type="text">
      <content textType="caption" paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(148, 148, 148, 1)" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>2014年入职第一天，带着大学四年机械设计与汽车构造的理论知识走进车间，第一次接触实车装配就遭遇了"纸上谈兵"的尴尬——图纸上清晰的"公差配合"，在生产线因焊接变形、零件来料误差变得"面目全非"。</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="36" topLeftX="70.12" topLeftY="289.28" type="text">
      <content paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="18" fontFamily="寒蝉德黑体" color="rgba(228, 228, 228, 1)" bold="false" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>理论与实践的差距</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="177.36" topLeftX="362.05" topLeftY="340.68" type="text">
      <content textType="caption" paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(148, 148, 148, 1)" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>参与某紧凑车型底盘装配项目时，严格按照设计图纸安装下摆臂衬套，结果80%的车辆出现转向异响。跟着资深工程师蹲守生产线3天，找到问题根源——忽略了低温环境下橡胶衬套的收缩特性。</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="36" topLeftX="362.05" topLeftY="289.28" type="text">
      <content paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="18" fontFamily="寒蝉德黑体" color="rgba(228, 228, 228, 1)" bold="false" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>底盘装配项目经历</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="177.36" topLeftX="654.12" topLeftY="340.68" type="text">
      <content textType="caption" paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(148, 148, 148, 1)" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>在衬套安装时特意留出了0.3mm的补偿间隙，异响问题彻底解决。这次经历让我意识到：汽车工程从不是单纯的理论推导，而是"实践的艺术"。</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="236" height="36" topLeftX="654.12" topLeftY="289.28" type="text">
