        <p>核心感悟</p>
      </content>
    </shape>
    <shape width="820" height="75" topLeftX="70.12" topLeftY="188.42" type="text">
      <content textType="caption" paddingTop="4" paddingBottom="4" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(148, 148, 148, 1)" backgroundColor="rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" bold="false" italic="false" underline="false" strikethrough="false" list="none" listStyle="circle-hollow-square" textAlign="left" autoFit="normal-auto-fit">
        <p>脱离了真实工况的理论，再完美也只是空中楼阁，只有把理论放进生产线的"熔炉"里淬炼，才能真正解决问题。</p>
      </content>
